# AI Model Test Datasets

This directory contains test datasets for AI model validation.

## Dataset Files

- `triage-test-dataset.json` - 10,000 labeled triage cases
- `vision-test-dataset.json` - 5,000 medical images with annotations
- `disease-prediction-dataset.json` - Historical outbreak data
- `cdss-test-dataset.json` - 8,000 clinical cases with expert recommendations

## Dataset Format

Each dataset includes:
- Input features
- Ground truth labels
- Demographic information
- Metadata (source, date, expert annotations)

## Data Privacy

All datasets are anonymized and comply with HIPAA and DISHA Act requirements.
No real patient data is used in testing.
